Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The number of casualties from the fire at the Friedrich\NEmmanuel Library at Munich University...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has now risen to five dead, thirty-four injured.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The search for the missing people still continues.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were able to interview some of those\Nrescued, so please have a look.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It became a sea of fire before I\Nrealized what was happening...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I was done for when I was surrounded\Nby all the smoke and couldn't breathe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone saved us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, he was Asian.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he alright?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He shot the hinges off the door and opened it for us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many more people would've \N died if he hadn't been there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The authorities have concluded that this\Nfire was set using oil and gasoline...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have announced that they will find the\Nperson responsible as soon as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:28.83,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(225,200)\pos(357,363)}The Hell In His Sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything burned nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite saying how books are the wisdom\Nand property of mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they burn, that's the end of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any fingerprints from the sniper rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it also burned, I'm not sure\Nif we'll find any fingerprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The model is most certainly the Mauser\NSR-93 that the Asian man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whom we believe to be Dr. Tenma ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since everything burned this badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be hard to find any traces of the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No scene is completely devoid of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a cuff link that was on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it to be analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can leave a place without leaving\Ntraces of his existence behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can, then he's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if by chance there's no evidence to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's no criminal we can't catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get an interview with Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's in the intensive care unit right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His burns aren't very serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he is rather old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're not allowing any visitors right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give you permission to question him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's conscious, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only be a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Schuwald is currently in a state of extreme shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs all the rest he can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Mr. Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my sympathies for this terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lunge from the German BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I asked the police earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's someone I'd like you to find for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the person who tried to assassinate your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe he would...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what I wanted to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please find Johan Liebert for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan... Liebert...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan should have attended the ceremony\Nat the library with my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't find him anywhere, \N no matter where I look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Johan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Johan Liebert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll request a search immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the room Johan Liebert was renting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already moved out about two weeks ago, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name wasn't in the registry at the law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not really a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you contacted his parents living in Offenbach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they weren't too friendly\Nwith their neighbors, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we try collecting fingerprints \N in this room anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No input data available...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a room with so few traces of the\Nperson who was living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Johan Liebert...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you weren't hurt too badly, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you worry, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they were pulling people out one\Nafter another, I didn't see you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I became really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised you were able to get out of\Nthat fire by yourself, with those injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the firefighters were surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because someone helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone helped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the last to come out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a Japanese doctor being treated\Nin a hospital around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were several Japanese men, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they were all businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he helped me when I was\Ncrushed under the drop curtain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nina...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nina!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was definitely there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that right before the fire broke out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you told the people attending the\Nceremony to evacuate, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sensed something beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong, Mr. Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it if I hold closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who tried to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are witnesses who say they\Ndefinitely saw him at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the witnesses, this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was trying to save the lives of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please contact us immediately \N if you remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the whereabouts of\Nyour secretary, Johan Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's gone completely senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's no surprise, after\Nhaving such a shock at his age...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it for the Vampire of Bayern,\Nthe Emperor of the Financial World.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the eyes of a man\Nwho understands everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try checking out the other witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a list of victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The testimonies say that the person we\Nbelieve to be Tenma was saving lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose this is another case\Nof his multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Fortner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something special about that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nina Fortner left the hospital this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The address listed in the police registry was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the one listed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Fortner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The daughter of the Fortners who\Nwere killed in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Current whereabouts unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for speaking to me \N of such difficult matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits perfectly with what Tenma says has\Nbeen going on for the past ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came here while investigating a string of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he left immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to assassinate Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, at that library...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Tenma was going to execute\Nhis assassination plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I rushed to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was that big fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know if Johan was there\Nor not, much less Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop chasing after Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone you can go up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the police aren't being compliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just get ready and fight with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth will be revealed one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tired, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay at my place and rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was there when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it happened, he was \N definitely there at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma was definitely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bread is Kaisersemmel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put roast ham and Gouda cheese on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tenma's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better when I eat something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma always said that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting nicer out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go on a vacation once you get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go to Asia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be a good change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, please take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fought long enough, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three... Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was hell in the eyes of a living man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that I want you\Nto tell a certain man for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Dresden...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man is waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dresden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So all I have to do is go to Dresden\Nand tell that person the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go right away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother must have hated me \N so very much, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't hate you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you come back from Dresden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you stay with me forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm very scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a town straight out of a fairy tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that you felt when you\Nlooked at this picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say whatever comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Gillen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in this book that Johan read,\Nand the reason why he fainted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any frogs in that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to rely on that BKA agent Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be wise if we c\N hanged our plan, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we bring any \N evidence to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must negotiate directly \N with the people in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but we must present\Nthe materials after we've...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,taken our time to completely \N back up our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taken our time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long would that take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, our information regarding\NJohan is too vague and inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schuwald, the one employing Johan as a secretary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he has some information, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schuwald still can't have any visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's his son, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he left for somewhere two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not definite, but amongst the\Ntestimonies of the witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are some who say that an Asian\Nman was helping people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Tenma's fingerprints were on the sniper rifle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that was said to be found at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no testimony will do us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long must we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the truth is revealed and the\Npolice start to make their move...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,already be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also lost an important friend, Richard, in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Johan cut his future short!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't back down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A town from a fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to stay here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Dr. Reichwein thanks for \N taking such good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.61,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,390)}Dresden \N (Saxony)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck on the third day either, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to wait at the station square, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I don't think I'll be able to meet\Nthe man you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Karl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who was plotting to kill your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what the police told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you from the top\Nof the building for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like the police are following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should... hurry up and run...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dresden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait at-the train station...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son Karl will give you a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and give me the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cedok Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Frogs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my father also said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the monster you are after is a twin..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"the mother of the twins..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"is alive in Prague."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:31.06,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:44.49,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:44.49,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:47.45,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:23:01.13,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:23:01.13,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:25.99,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:34.41,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.87,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
